title: BONUS: Dorms and Ghoulsmashing Commentary
description:
Hey all! To celebrate the launch of the MBMBaM Seeso show on iTunes internationally, we're releasing a commentary track for the first episode. Enjoy!

Music: Dancing in Heaven by Q-Feel
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy)
